The OMAS cohiba LE has been designed in partnership with Corporación Habanos, S.A. Its shape is inspired by COHIBA cigar, and it might also be the best cigar theme pen produced. The COHIBA LIMITED EDITION by OMAS Writing Instrument Collection is composed by 1,966 pieces: 1,000 piston-filled fountain pens and 966 Roller Balls as a tribute to the year of foundation of COHIBA brand.
